{"tid":1758651,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"善用「增選委員」制度　擴大區議會優勢","createTime":"2019-11-27T07:48:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T03:05:52.000Z","uid":6497,"like":149,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"73be1da5bc134963c928d0578fc1b51be8b48279","tid":1758651,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:48:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191108/60240548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191108%2F60240548&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=71bc60ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191108%2F60240548&h=59604739\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191108/60240548</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1053235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1053235&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=9a0279b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1053235&h=a0681f2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1053235</a><br />\n<br />\n增選委員<br />\n職能上面同區議員有同等發言權和投票權<br />\n但唔係用民選方法辦生<br />\n而係區議會內以各個委員會自行協商產生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去保皇黨一直用呢個方式<br />\n黎幫自己友敗部復活或者做青訓嘅手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得今次區選搶到主導權<br />\n加上亦有唔少係新手素人<br />\n正正可以運用增選委員去引入更多對特定地區議題嘅同路人入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者幫岩岩挑戰失敗嘅手足重返議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進一步孤立會上建制派<br />\n同埋彌補現時素人區議員嘅不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3555d61e6816fcdade49477bb04fae1dfc15f514","tid":1758651,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":81,"score":-77,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一嚟就搞啲有違民主嘅嘢，你冇病?"},{"pid":"d1f337ab188986650052e9cea07d44eb58567415","tid":1758651,"uid":66260,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"3555d61e6816fcdade49477bb04fae1dfc15f514","tid":1758651,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":81,"score":-77,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一嚟就搞啲有違民主嘅嘢，你冇病?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:28:57.000Z","msg":"對住反民主既人就要用反民主既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貪官奸, 清官更加要奸"},{"pid":"986adb022c3d29be8f576008964e9c8ed5447be5","tid":1758651,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:30:14.000Z","msg":"拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共產黨咁"},{"pid":"3e8958274f54cf0335efb0b2ea2b836ddeed77dd","tid":1758651,"uid":53498,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"3555d61e6816fcdade49477bb04fae1dfc15f514","tid":1758651,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":81,"score":-77,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一嚟就搞啲有違民主嘅嘢，你冇病?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:31:53.000Z","msg":"你去中南海靜坐,用愛與和平感動支那共產党啦"},{"pid":"3ae89419087a1401a4133a51127e98b9066b9ef7","tid":1758651,"uid":5220,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"3555d61e6816fcdade49477bb04fae1dfc15f514","tid":1758651,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":81,"score":-77,"citedBy":14