gmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去保皇黨一直用呢個方式<br />\n黎幫自己友敗部復活或者做青訓嘅手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得今次區選搶到主導權<br />\n加上亦有唔少係新手素人<br />\n正正可以運用增選委員去引入更多對特定地區議題嘅同路人入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者幫岩岩挑戰失敗嘅手足重返議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進一步孤立會上建制派<br />\n同埋彌補現時素人區議員嘅不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"唔係wo ,你邊個區輸左少少既手足，真喺可以考慮問佢地想唔想做增選委員。<br />\n<br />\n北區，沙田都有幾席輸得唔抵。"},{"pid":"4c88eea3b2475486f1b3178b918332bb608f6336","tid":1758651,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e78a5d66e127c89245c7c2c63595028f52ff45","tid":1758651,"uid":47113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"73be1da5bc134963c928d0578fc1b51be8b48279","tid":1758651,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:48:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191108/60240548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191108%2F60240548&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=71bc60ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191108%2F60240548&h=59604739\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191108/60240548</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1053235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1053235&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=9a0279b6\"