ediahk.net/node/1053235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1053235&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=9a0279b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1053235&h=a0681f2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1053235</a><br />\n<br />\n增選委員<br />\n職能上面同區議員有同等發言權和投票權<br />\n但唔係用民選方法辦生<br />\n而係區議會內以各個委員會自行協商產生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去保皇黨一直用呢個方式<br />\n黎幫自己友敗部復活或者做青訓嘅手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得今次區選搶到主導權<br />\n加上亦有唔少係新手素人<br />\n正正可以運用增選委員去引入更多對特定地區議題嘅同路人入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者幫岩岩挑戰失敗嘅手足重返議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進一步孤立會上建制派<br />\n同埋彌補現時素人區議員嘅不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:47:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b043e40a13cb990601cadd0bcef02de63eab795","tid":1758651,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a68859592e70cb86b6d4f9c308bfdb0c0fb00b8c","tid":1758651,"uid":326897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3555d61e6816fcdade49477bb04fae1dfc15f514","tid":1758651,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":81,"score":-77,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一嚟就搞啲有違民主嘅嘢，你冇病?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime